453/size6/706e9a91817b751b262f7698d03c12f9.jpg","text":"እንቁራሪትና እባብ\nበጠዋት መንገዳቸውን\nጀመሩ፡፡ ወደ ደን\nውስጥም ገቡ፡፡","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128454/size6/22fe9466ce5ee340a47e992535f75bb7.jpg","text":"የአይጠመጎጥ መንጋ\nአገኙ፡፡ እባብ ፈራ፡፡","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128455/size6/f1f8788de491db045f70288a3b2086d1.jpg","text":"እንቁራሪት ጓደኛዋን\nአዳነችው፡፡","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128462/size6/a671c06769bcce71ebfc96e94373f14e.jpg","text":"እናቷ ቤት ሲደርሱ\nእርቧቸው ነበር፡፡","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128467/size6/0dd573ca6bb31c8ade52bc743b5eec1c.jpg","text":"እጃቸውን ታጥበው\nለመብላት ተዘጋጁ፡፡","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128471/size6/315bfa80749670593d1f286ae05116c6.jpg","text":"‹‹እባብ፣ እባክህ\nተቀመጥ›› አለችው\nእንቁራሪት፡፡","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128472/size6/02994535e9bb0c1de24dbee66eceeb36.jpg","text":"እባብ ለመቀመጥ ሞከረ፡፡\nግን እንቁራት ስላልሆነ\nአልቻለም፡፡","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128473/size6/6208965123e7835364d9e2669ec4d41f.jpg","text":"‹‹እኔ እንደ እንቁራት\nመቀመጥ አልችልበትም››\nአለ እባቡ፡፡","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128474/size6/a7010c15c73a806a8bf9118763c44d08.jpg","text":"እንቁራት አልሰማችውም፡፡","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128475/size6/34d1683dd60cfea2a82a18abd1138cea.jpg","text":"‹‹ልትረጂኝ ስላልቻልሽ\nወደ ቤቴ እሄዳለሁ፡፡››","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128476/size6/f03cfbefddfd30830411d83b4f54